cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "snark — Sarcasm as a Service"
message: "If you reference or build on this project, please cite it using these metadata."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Kodag
    given-names: Pramod
abstract: >-
  A public, AGPL-licensed AI humor and utility API where every response is
  uniquely generated by a large language model. It uses a provider-abstraction
  layer with an automatic fallback chain across Groq, Gemini, and Claude,
  IP-based rate limiting, and no authentication.
repository-code: "https://github.com/PramodTKodag/snark"
